{
  "video_id": "AkUcaludrcI",
  "title": "A young scientist's quest for clean water | Deepika Kurup",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12540.0,
      "end_time": 17235.0,
      "text": "Every summer, my family and I travel across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19116.0,
      "text": "3,000 miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19140.0,
      "end_time": 21740.0,
      "text": "to the culturally diverse country of India."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22580.0,
      "end_time": 26939.0,
      "text": "Now, India is a country infamous for its scorching heat and humidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27580.0,
      "end_time": 32190.0,
      "text": "For me, the only relief from this heat is to drink plenty of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32740.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34236.0,
      "text": "Now, while in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 38739.0,
      "text": "my parents always remind me to only drink boiled or bottled water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39220.0,
      "end_time": 41476.0,
      "text": "because unlike here in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41500.0,
      "end_time": 45700.0,
      "text": "where I can just turn on a tap and easily get clean, potable water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46300.0,
      "end_time": 48820.0,
      "text": "in India, the water is often contaminated."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51156.0,
      "text": "So my parents have to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51180.0,
      "end_time": 53140.0,
      "text": "that the water we drink is safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54300.0,
      "end_time": 56675.0,
      "text": "However, I soon realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56700.0,
      "end_time": 59356.0,
      "text": "that not everyone is fortunate enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59380.0,
      "end_time": 61820.0,
      "text": "to enjoy the clean water we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62980.0,
      "end_time": 67196.0,
      "text": "Outside my grandparents&#39; house in the busy streets of India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67220.0,
      "end_time": 69876.0,
      "text": "I saw people standing in long lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69900.0,
      "end_time": 71596.0,
      "text": "under the hot sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71620.0,
      "end_time": 73900.0,
      "text": "filling buckets with water from a tap."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75180.0,
      "end_time": 77156.0,
      "text": "I even saw children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77180.0,
      "end_time": 79836.0,
      "text": "who looked the same age as me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79860.0,
      "end_time": 82236.0,
      "text": "filling up these clear plastic bottles"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 85340.0,
      "text": "with dirty water from streams on the roadside."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86700.0,
      "end_time": 88396.0,
      "text": "Watching these kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88420.0,
      "end_time": 90556.0,
      "text": "forced to drink water"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90580.0,
      "end_time": 93596.0,
      "text": "that I felt was too dirty to touch"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93620.0,
      "end_time": 95780.0,
      "text": "changed my perspective on the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96860.0,
      "end_time": 100396.0,
      "text": "This unacceptable social injustice"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100420.0,
      "end_time": 103476.0,
      "text": "compelled me to want to find a solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 105460.0,
      "text": "to our world&#39;s clean water problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106660.0,
      "end_time": 109916.0,
      "text": "I wanted to know why these kids lacked water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109940.0,
      "end_time": 112380.0,
      "text": "a substance that is essential for life."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112820.0,
      "end_time": 115760.0,
      "text": "And I learned that we are facing"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115100.0,
      "end_time": 117460.0,
      "text": "a global water crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118540.0,
      "end_time": 120356.0,
      "text": "Now, this may seem surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120380.0,
      "end_time": 124476.0,
      "text": "as 75 percent of our planet is covered in water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124500.0,
      "end_time": 128556.0,
      "text": "but only 2.5 percent of that is freshwater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128580.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132516.0,
      "text": "and less than one percent of Earth&#39;s freshwater supply"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132540.0,
      "end_time": 134500.0,
      "text": "is available for human consumption."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135580.0,
      "end_time": 137276.0,
      "text": "With rising populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137300.0,
      "end_time": 140275.0,
      "text": "industrial development and economic growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140299.0,
      "end_time": 143760.0,
      "text": "our demand for clean water is increasing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143100.0,
      "end_time": 146299.0,
      "text": "yet our freshwater resources are rapidly depleting."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147660.0,
      "end_time": 150276.0,
      "text": "According to the World Health Organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150300.0,
      "end_time": 154196.0,
      "text": "660 million people in our world"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154220.0,
      "end_time": 156820.0,
      "text": "lack access to a clean water source."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157780.0,
      "end_time": 161760.0,
      "text": "Lack of access to clean water is a leading cause of death"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161100.0,
      "end_time": 164116.0,
      "text": "in children under the age of five in developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164140.0,
      "end_time": 167595.0,
      "text": "and UNICEF estimates that 3,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167620.0,
      "end_time": 170340.0,
      "text": "die every day from a water-related disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172100.0,
      "end_time": 175476.0,
      "text": "So after returning home one summer in eighth grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175500.0,
      "end_time": 178596.0,
      "text": "I decided that I wanted to combine my passion"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178620.0,
      "end_time": 180756.0,
      "text": "for solving the global water crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 180780.0,
      "end_time": 182780.0,
      "text": "with my interest in science."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185396.0,
      "text": "So I decided that the best thing to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185420.0,
      "end_time": 189339.0,
      "text": "would be to convert my garage into a laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 190980.0,
      "end_time": 192956.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192980.0,
      "end_time": 196835.0,
      "text": "Actually, at first I converted my kitchen into a laboratory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196860.0,
      "end_time": 199700.0,
      "text": "but my parents didn&#39;t really approve and kicked me out."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201220.0,
      "end_time": 205676.0,
      "text": "I also read a lot of journal papers on water-related research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205700.0,
      "end_time": 208555.0,
      "text": "and I learned that currently in developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 208580.0,
      "end_time": 210996.0,
      "text": "something called solar disinfection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211200.0,
      "end_time": 213980.0,
      "text": "or SODIS, is used to purify water."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 214820.0,
      "end_time": 219636.0,
      "text": "In SODIS, clear plastic bottles are filled with contaminated water"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219660.0,
      "end_time": 222579.0,
      "text": "and then exposed to sunlight for six to eight hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223340.0,
      "end_time": 225356.0,
      "text": "The UV radiation from the sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 225380.0,
      "end_time": 228835.0,
      "text": "destroys the DNA of these harmful pathogens"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228860.0,
      "end_time": 230820.0,
      "text": "and decontaminates the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231700.0,
      "end_time": 235435.0,
      "text": "Now, while SODIS is really easy to use and energy-efficient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235460.0,
      "end_time": 237756.0,
      "text": "as it only uses solar energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 237780.0,
      "end_time": 239156.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s really slow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 239180.0,
      "end_time": 241940.0,
      "text": "as it can take up to two days when it&#39;s cloudy."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 242780.0,
      "end_time": 245876.0,
      "text": "So in order to make the SODIS process faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245900.0,
      "end_time": 249196.0,
      "text": "this new method called photocatalysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249220.0,
      "end_time": 250859.0,
      "text": "has recently been used."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 251460.0,
      "end_time": 254316.0,
      "text": "So what exactly is this photocatalysis?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 254340.0,
      "end_time": 255556.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s break it down:"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 255580.0,
      "end_time": 257236.0,
      "text": "\"photo\" means from the sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260300.0,
      "text": "and a catalyst is something that speeds up a reaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260860.0,
      "end_time": 263360.0,
      "text": "So what photocatalysis is doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263600.0,
      "end_time": 266220.0,
      "text": "is it&#39;s just speeding up this solar disinfection process."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267220.0,
      "end_time": 270556.0,
      "text": "When sunlight comes in and strikes a photocatalyst,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 270580.0,
      "end_time": 274195.0,
      "text": "like TiO2, or titanium dioxide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 274220.0,
      "end_time": 277636.0,
      "text": "it creates these really reactive oxygen species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 277660.0,
      "end_time": 281940.0,
      "text": "like superoxides, hydrogen peroxide and hydroxyl radicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282740.0,
      "end_time": 284636.0,
      "text": "These reactive oxygen species"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 284660.0,
      "end_time": 287556.0,
      "text": "are able to remove bacteria and organics"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 287580.0,
      "end_time": 290539.0,
      "text": "and a whole lot of contaminants from drinking water."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291740.0,
      "end_time": 294956.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately, there are several disadvantages"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 294980.0,
      "end_time": 298860.0,
      "text": "to the way photocatalytic SODIS is currently deployed."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299460.0,
      "end_time": 302596.0,
      "text": "See, what they do is they take the clear plastic bottles"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302620.0,
      "end_time": 306600.0,
      "text": "and they coat the inside with this photocatalytic coating."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 307200.0,
      "end_time": 310316.0,
      "text": "But photocatalysts like titanium dioxide"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 310340.0,
      "end_time": 313360.0,
      "text": "are actually commonly used in sunscreens"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 313600.0,
      "end_time": 314700.0,
      "text": "to block UV radiation."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 315140.0,
      "end_time": 317996.0,
      "text": "So when they&#39;re coated on the inside of these bottles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 318200.0,
      "end_time": 320796.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re actually blocking some of the UV radiation"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 320820.0,
      "end_time": 323380.0,
      "text": "and diminishing the efficiency of the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 324380.0,
      "end_time": 326516.0,
      "text": "Also, these photocatalytic coatings"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326540.0,
      "end_time": 329396.0,
      "text": "are not tightly bound to the plastic bottle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 329420.0,
      "end_time": 333340.0,
      "text": "which means they wash off, and people end up drinking the catalyst."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 334340.0,
      "end_time": 336996.0,
      "text": "While TiO2 is safe and inert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 337200.0,
      "end_time": 339756.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s really inefficient if you keep drinking the catalyst,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 339780.0,
      "end_time": 342155.0,
      "text": "because then you have to continue to replenish it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 342180.0,
      "end_time": 343660.0,
      "text": "even after a few uses."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 347515.0,
      "text": "So my goal was to overcome the disadvantages"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 347540.0,
      "end_time": 349556.0,
      "text": "of these current treatment methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 349580.0,
      "end_time": 351835.0,
      "text": "and create a safe, sustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 351860.0,
      "end_time": 355780.0,
      "text": "cost-effective and eco-friendly method of purifying water."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 356940.0,
      "end_time": 359996.0,
      "text": "What started off as an eighth grade science fair project"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360200.0,
      "end_time": 364419.0,
      "text": "is now my photocatalytic composite for water purification."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 365260.0,
      "end_time": 368900.0,
      "text": "The composite combines titanium dioxide with cement."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 369660.0,
      "end_time": 373636.0,
      "text": "The cement-like composite can be formed into several different shapes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 373660.0,
      "end_time": 377340.0,
      "text": "which results in an extremely versatile range of deployment methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377980.0,
      "end_time": 380360.0,
      "text": "For example, you could create a rod"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 380600.0,
      "end_time": 383740.0,
      "text": "that can easily be placed inside water bottles for individual use"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 384380.0,
      "end_time": 388900.0,
      "text": "or you could create a porous filter that can filter water for families."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 389620.0,
      "end_time": 393360.0,
      "text": "You can even coat the inside of an existing water tank"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 393600.0,
      "end_time": 394916.0,
      "text": "to purify larger amounts of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394940.0,
      "end_time": 397900.0,
      "text": "for communities over a longer period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 399460.0,
      "end_time": 401395.0,
      "text": "Now, over the course of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 401420.0,
      "end_time": 403876.0,
      "text": "my journey hasn&#39;t really been easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 403900.0,
      "end_time": 407275.0,
      "text": "You know, I didn&#39;t have access to a sophisticated laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 407300.0,
      "end_time": 410796.0,
      "text": "I was 14 years old when I started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 410820.0,
      "end_time": 413156.0,
      "text": "but I didn&#39;t let my age deter me"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 413180.0,
      "end_time": 416360.0,
      "text": "in my interest in pursuing scientific research"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 416600.0,
      "end_time": 418540.0,
      "text": "and wanting to solve the global water crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 419620.0,
      "end_time": 423436.0,
      "text": "See, water isn&#39;t just the universal solvent."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 423460.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "Water is a universal human right."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 426980.0,
      "end_time": 428236.0,
      "text": "And for that reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 432436.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m continuing to work on this science fair project from 2012"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 432460.0,
      "end_time": 435635.0,
      "text": "to bring it from the laboratory into the real world."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 435660.0,
      "end_time": 439116.0,
      "text": "And this summer, I founded Catalyst for World Water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 439140.0,
      "end_time": 444419.0,
      "text": "a social enterprise aimed at catalyzing solutions to the global water crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 445100.0,
      "end_time": 446980.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 452600.0,
      "end_time": 456360.0,
      "text": "Alone, a single drop of water can&#39;t do much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 456600.0,
